trans-unit.source: Panic Control monitors your pages and checks whether they are up or down. This check uptime is highly configurable
If your website goes down an email is sent to you and your team. You can add multiple addresses to sent the alerts
You don't like our email template or you want create your own template? Let's go! You are welcome!
